-polices-closure-report-5583784%5C%22%3Ethe%20Telangana%20police%20claim%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Rohith%20was%20not%20Dalit%20and%20that%20it%20was%20likely%20the%20fear%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Breal%20caste%26quot%3B%20being%20revealed%20that%20led%20him%20to%20suicide.%20At%20the%20core%20of%20this%20claim%20are%20some%20formalities%20of%20law%20and%20policy%20that%20must%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScheduled%20Castes%20(SC)%20status%20is%20legally%20determined%20by%20ancestry.%20More%20specifically%2C%20the%20bloodlines%20of%20men%20are%20the%20carriages%20of%20caste.%20That%20is%20to%20say%2C%20formal%20legal%20procedures%20require%20the%20SC%20certification%20of%20a%20father%20to%20grant%20an%20SC%20certificate%20to%20a%20child.%20This%20patriarchal%20character%20of%20law%20and%20policy%20has%20been%20contested%20in%20courts.%20As%20a%20result%20of%20judicial%20interventions%2C%20a%20mother's%20SC%20certification%20can%20be%20admitted%20for%20certifying%20a%20child's%20SC%20status.%20But%20this%20is%20an%20exception%2C%20not%20a%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Process%20Of%20Humiliation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESC%20certifications%20at%20local%20governance%20levels%20have%20also%20changed%20over%20time.%20Plus%2C%20sometimes%2C%20these%20certifications%20can%20be%20outcomes%20of%20discretionary%20functions%20of%20power.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20SC%20certifications%20could%20be%20granted%20based%20on%20supporting%20statements%20of%20gazetted%20government%20officers%20and%20ordinary%20neighbours%20too.%20In%20cases%20where%20neither%20parent%20has%20a%20formal%20caste%20certificate%2C%20that%20ordeal%20is%20worse%20as%20an%20individual%C2%A0-%C2%A0%20especially%20interstate%20migrant%20workers%C2%A0-%20runs%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20trying%20to%20get%20their%20caste%20identity%20certified.%20All%20such%20processes%20inadvertently%20end%20up%20imposing%20varying%20degrees%20of%20humiliation%20upon%20those%20who%20want%20to%20obtain%20SC%20certification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-name-is-rohith-vemula-i-am-a-dalit-he-said-in-video-days-before-he-died-1475243%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%20'My%20Name%20Is%20Rohith%20Vemula.%20I%20Am%20A%20Dalit%2C'%20He%20Said%20In%20Video%20Days%20Before%20He%20Died%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20kind%20of%20humiliation%20has%20been%20playing%20out%20openly%20for%20anyone%20to%20see%2C%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Rohith%20Vemula%20and%20his%20mother%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fshows%2Findia-matters%2Frohith-vemula-his-mother-s-son-445670%5C%22%3ERadhika%20Vemula%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Born%20to%20SC%20Mala%20parents%2C%20Radhika%20was%20adopted%20by%20an%20Other%20Backward%20Class%20(OBC)%20Vaddera%20woman%2C%20and%20later%2C%20she%20married%20a%20Vaddera%20man.%20Despite%20the%20two%20legalities%20-%20adoption%20and%20marriage%20-%20Radhika%20could%20retain%20her%20SC%20status%20because%20of%20the%20bloodline%20of%20her%20SC%20Mala%20father.%20Furthermore%2C%20Radhika%20later%20returned%20to%20her%20SC%20community%20after%20leaving%20her%20OBC%20husband.%20Patriarchy%20is%20so%20deeply%20entrenched%20in%20law%20and%20policy%20that%20Rohith%20Vemula's%20caste%20is%20now%20determined%20by%20the%20caste%20of%20an%20absent%20OBC%20father%2C%20not%20his%20present%20SC%20mother.%20Ultimately%2C%20legality%20here%20appears%20to%20operate%20as%20an%20informal%20tool%20for%20imposing%20humiliation%20and%20adding%20insult%20to%20injury%20at%20mass%20levels%20of%20Dalit%20consciousness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20%3Cem%3ESujata%20%3C%2Fem%3EStory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBimal%20Roy's%20famous%20movie%20%3Cem%3ESujata%20%3C%2Fem%3E(1959)%20is%20something%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20current%20fanciful%20speculation%20about%20Rohith%20Vemula's%20caste%20identity.%20An%20%26quot%3Buntouchable%26quot%3B%20orphan%20baby%20girl%20is%20adopted%20into%20a%20Savarna%20household.%20This%20girl%20is%20named%20Sujata.%20She's%20humiliated%20and%20abused%20routinely%20and%20grows%20up%20as%20an%20exploited%2C%20unpaid%20household%20servant.%20The%20movie%20ends%20on%20a%20Cinderella-like%20happy%20note%2C%20with%20Sujata's%20marriage%20to%20a%20Savarna%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20hypothetically%2C%20a%20sequel%20to%20%3Cem%3ESujata%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecould%20show%20her%20as%20a%20happy%20wife%20of%20this%20Savarna%20man%20and%20a%20mother%20to%20their%20children%2C%20but%20somehow%2C%20she%20continues%20to%20be%20humiliated%20and%20abused%20and%20remains%20an%20exploited%2C%20unpaid%20servant%20in%20her%20marital%20home.%20This%20sequel%20would%20also%20end%20happily%20but%20on%20a%20more%20realistic%20note%3A%20Sujata%20leaving%20her%20Savarna%20husband%2C%20taking%20her%20children%20and%20returning%20to%20her%20%26quot%3Buntouchable%26quot%3B%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frohith-vemulas-mother-asked-to-prove-she-belongs-to-scheduled-caste-1659522%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0Rohith%20Vemula's%20Mother%20Asked%20To%20Prove%20She%20Belongs%20To%20Scheduled%20Caste%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Cem%3ESujata%203%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20woman%20could%20raise%20these%20children%20as%20proud%20Dalits%2C%20but%20the%20patriarchal%20forces%20of%20the%20law%20would%20impose%20Savarna%20caste%20ancestry%20on%20them%2C%20denying%20and%20obliterating%20their%20matrilineal%20Dalit%20bloodline.%20The%20script%20of%20%3Cem%3ESujata%203%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20what's%20currently%20being%20written%2C%20and%20the%20ending%20is%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201959%20%3Cem%3ESujata%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20its%20hypothetical%20sequels%20outlined%20here%20are%20relatable%20conjectures%20into%20the%20life%20of%20Radhika%20Vemula.%20These%20are%20not%20claims%20to%20determine%20her%20reality.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20Telangana%20police%20should%20not%20be%20the%20ultimate%20arbiters%20to%20determine%20the%20%26quot%3Breal%20caste%26quot%3B%20of%20Rohith%20Vemula.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20point%20in%20both%20the%20reality%20and%20the%20fiction%20around%20Rohith%20Vemula's%20suicide%20is%20that%20the%20law%20and%20policy%20for%20SC%20certification%20must%20accept%20matrilineal%20bloodlines.%20This%20is%20not%20just%20a%20theoretical%20debate%20but%20a%20constitutional%20caste%20matter%20-%20related%20to%20equality%20and%20non-discrimination%20based%20on%20sex%20-%20with%20real-life%20implications%20for%20individuals%20like%20Rohith%20Vemula.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Prof.%20Dr%20Sumit%20Baudh%20(they%2Fhe)%20teaches%20Caste%20Law%20and%20Representation%2C%20Intersectionality%20Applications%20and%20Analysis%2C%20among%20other%20courses%2C%20and%20tweets%20on%20X%20%40BaudhSumit)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715234040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fvideo%2Fimages%2Fvod%2Fmedium%2F2017-01%2Fbig_445670_1484248116.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frohith-vemula-and-his-dalit-identity-reality-vs-fiction-5622717%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20law%20and%20policy%20for%20Scheduled%20Caste%20certification%20must%20accept%20matrilineal%20bloodline%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frohith-vemula-and-his-dalit-identity-reality-vs-fiction-5622717%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Has%20Savarkar%20crossed%20Rs%2025%20cr%20mark%20in%2050%20days%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715234021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109969623%2Cimgsize-26464.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollyw