%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vesna%20Vulovic%20Survived%20The%20Highest%20Fall%20Ever%20With%20No%20Parachute%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHistory%20is%20full%20of%20incidents%20that%20show%20people's%20courage%20and%20resilience.%20But%20there%20are%20very%20few%20stories%20that%20shine%20as%20brightly%20as%20that%20of%20Vesna%20Vulovic.%20Her%20remarkable%20journey%20from%20tragedy%20to%20triumph%20serves%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20indomitable%20human%20spirit.%20Ms%20Vulovic%20was%20working%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant%20onboard%20JAT%20Yugoslav%20Airlines'%20Flight%20367%20on%20January%2026%2C%201972%2C%20when%20a%20suspected%20bomb%20brought%20down%20the%20plane%20among%20the%20mountains%20over%20Czechoslovakia%20-%20now%20known%20as%20the%20Czech%20Republic.%20All%2027%20other%20passengers%20and%20crew%20died%20but%20Ms%20Vulovic%20survived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-38427411%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20plane%20exploded%20mid-air%20but%20Ms%20Vulovic%20survived%20the%2033%2C000-foot%20fall%2C%20the%20highest%20recorded%20fall%20without%20a%20parachute%20in%20aviation%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20investigators%20later%20said%20that%20she%20was%20trapped%20by%20a%20food%20cart%20in%20the%20plane's%20tail%20section%20as%20it%20plummeted%20to%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tail%20landed%20in%20a%20snow-blanketed%20and%20forested%20area%20that%20was%20thought%20to%20have%20cushioned%20the%20impact%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Vulovic's%20screams%20were%20heard%20by%20Bruno%20Honke%2C%20a%20woodsman.%20She%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%20where%20she%20fell%20into%20a%20coma%20for%2010%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Vulovic%20suffered%20a%20fractured%20skull%2C%20two%20crushed%20vertebrae%20and%20she%20also%20broke%20her%20pelvis%2C%20several%20ribs%20and%20both%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20broken%2C%20and%20the%20doctors%20put%20me%20back%20together%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20temporarily%20paralysed%20from%20the%20waist%20down%20by%20the%20fall%2C%20but%20she%20never%20surrendered%20to%20despair.%20Ms%20Vulovic%20made%20a%20near-full%20recovery%20and%20returned%20to%20work%20for%20the%20airline%20in%20a%20desk%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20miraculous%20survival%20earned%20her%20a%20place%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fnews%2F2022%2F4%2Fhow-vesna-vulovic-survived-the-highest-fall-ever-with-no-parachute-697786%5C%22%3EGuinness%20Book%20of%20Records%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201985.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20no%20recollection%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20continued%20to%20fly%20as%20a%20passenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Vulovic's%20harrowing%20experience%20transformed%20her%20into%20a%20symbol%20of%20hope%20and%20reconciliation%2C%20and%20a%20celebrity%20in%20Serbia.%20She%20dedicated%20her%20life%20to%20advocating%20for%20peace%2C%20bridging%20divides%2C%20and%20fostering%20understanding%20among%20people%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Vulovic%20channelled%20her%20fame%20into%20campaigning%20for%20political%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20like%20a%20cat%2C%20I%20have%20had%20nine%20lives.%20But%20if%20nationalist%20forces%20in%20this%20country%20prevail%2C%20my%20heart%20will%20burst%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Vulovic%20died%20in%202016%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2066.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715233740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fvl1bt5ko_vesna-voluvic_625x300_09_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fflight-attendant-survived-33-000-feet-fall-with-no-parachute-read-vesna