low-cost%20airline%2C%20which%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20Air%20India%2C%20now%20owned%20by%20the%20Tata%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20employees%20have%20been%20protesting%20against%20the%20new%20employment%20terms%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20The%20crew%2C%20the%20sources%20said%2C%20has%20alleged%20a%20lack%20of%20equality%20in%20the%20treatment%20of%20staff.%20They%20have%20claimed%20that%20some%20staff%20members%20have%20been%20offered%20lower%20job%20roles%20despite%20clearing%20interviews%20for%20senior%20positions%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%20The%20crew%20has%20also%20flagged%20some%20modifications%20in%20their%20compensation%20package.%20These%20developments%20are%20taking%20place%20even%20as%20the%20airline%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20merger%20with%20AIX%20Connect%20(formerly%20AirAsia%20India).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20India%20Express%20crisis%20is%20fresh%20trouble%20for%20the%20Tata%20group%2C%20barely%20a%20month%20after%20its%20full-service%20carrier%20Vistara%20witnessed%20disruptions%20due%20to%20protests%20by%20pilots%20over%20a%20host%20of%20issues%2C%20including%20their%20rostering%20for%20flights%20and%20changes%20in%20their%20pay%20packages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Air%20India%20Express%20spokesperson%20yesterday%20said%20the%20management%20is%20engaging%20with%20the%20crew%20to%20understand%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20mass%20leave%20and%20added%20that%20they%20are%20working%20to%20minimise%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20fliers.%20The%20airline%20management%20plans%20to%20hold%20a%20townhall%20with%20cabin%20crew%20members%20today.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20termination%20letter%20issued%20to%20the%2030-odd%20crew%20members%20says%20that%20the%20mass%20leave%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20points%20to%20a%20pre-meditated%20and%20concerted%20abstention%20from%20work%20without%20any%20justifiable%20reason%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20above%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20flights%20had%20to%20be%20cancelled%20thereby%20disrupting%20the%20entire%20schedule%2C%20which%20caused%20tremendous%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20Company's%20esteemed%20passengers.%20Your%20act%20is%20not%20only%20subversive%20of%20public%20interest%2C%20but%20has%20also%20caused%20embarrassment%2C%20severe%20reputational%20damage%2C%20and%20serious%20monetary%20loss%20to%20the%20Company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYour%20act%20of%20reporting%20sick%20for%20work%20amounts%20to%20a%20concerted%20action%20with%20a%20common%20understanding%2C%20to%20not%20operate%20the%20flight%20and%20to%20disrupt%20services%20of%20the%20Company.%20This%20is%20not%20only%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20applicable%20laws%2C%20but%20also%20violates%20the%20Air%20India%20Express%20Limited%20Employees'%20Service%20Rules%20as%20are%20applicable%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20India%20Express%20Employees%20Union%20(AIXEU)%2C%20an%20organisation%20claiming%20to%20represent%20the%20crew%20members%2C%20has%20written%20to%20the%20management%20and%20%26quot%3Bhighlighted%20a%20stark%20departure%20from%20commitments%26quot%3B.%20The%20union%20has%20accused%20the%20airline%20of%20mismanagement%20and%20treating%20staff%20unequally.%20Sources%20from%20Air%20India%20Express%2C%20however%2C%20have%20said%20it%20does%20not%20recognise%20any%20employees'%20union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20regional%20labour%20commissioner%20has%20weighed%20in%20and%20said%20the%20staff's%20grievances%20were%20genuine.%C2%A0In%20a%20May%203%20e-mail%20to%20Air%20India%20Chairman%20Natarajan%20Chandrasekaran%20and%20others%20-%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20NDTV%20-%20the%20Regional%20Labour%20Commissioner%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Ashok%20Perumalla%2C%20pointed%20to%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20violations%20of%20labour%20laws%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20Union%20are%20genuine%2C%20Mr%20Perumulla%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20management%20of%