olls%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20aims%20to%20destabilise%20India%20during%20the%202024%20general%20election%2C%20the%20Russian%20foreign%20ministry%20has%20said%20after%20a%20US%20federal%20commission's%20report%20criticised%20New%20Delhi%20for%20alleged%20violations%20of%20religious%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERT%20news%2C%20a%20Russian%20government-owned%20news%20network%2C%20has%20reported%20that%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Maria%20Zakharova%20has%20said%20Washington%20lacks%20understanding%20of%20India's%20national%20mentality%20and%20history%20and%20continues%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Bunfounded%20accusations%26quot%3B%20about%20religious%20freedoms%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BUnfounded%20Accusations%3A%26quot%3B%20US%20Aims%20to%20Destabilise%20India%20During%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FLokSabha2024%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23LokSabha2024%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20Russian%20Foreign%20Ministry%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSpox%20Maria%20Zakharova%20has%20said%20Washington%20lacks%20simple%20understanding%20of%20India's%20national%20mentality%20and%20history%2C%20as%20America%20continues%20to%20make%20%26quot%3Bunfounded%20accusations%26quot%3B%20about%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FM8G0gtiP92%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FM8G0gtiP92%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20RT_India%20(%40RT_India_news)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRT_India_news%2Fstatus%2F1788203969954840747%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZakharova%20called%20it%20disrespectful%20to%20India%20as%20a%20country%20and%20a%20State.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20%5Bbehind%20the%20US%20accusations%5D%20is%20to%20unbalance%20the%20internal%20political%20situation%20in%20India%20and%20complicate%20the%20general%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20RT%20news%20quoted%20her%20as%20saying.%C2%A0The%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20added%20that%20Washington's%20actions%20clearly%20constitute%20interference%20in%20India's%20internal%20affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20the%20latest%20annual%20report%20by%20the%20United%20States%20Commission%20on%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%20(USCIRF)%20criticised%20India%20for%20alleged%20violations%20of%20religious%20freedom.%20The%20commission%20also%20renewed%20its%20recommendation%20to%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20State%20to%20declare%20India%20a%20%26quot%3BCountry%20of%20Particular%20Concern%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20has%20accused%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20of%20reinforcing%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%26quot%3B%20nationalist%20policies.%20It%20has%20also%20flagged%20the%20continued%20enforcement%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%20Foreign%20Contribution%20(Regulation)%20Act%2C%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20and%20anti-conversion%20and%20cow-slaughter%20laws.%20The%20enforcement%20of%20these%20laws%2C%20it%20has%20said%2C%20has%20resulted%20in%20arbitrary%20detention%2C%20monitoring%20and%20targeting%20of%20religious%20minorities%20and%20those%20advocating%20on%20their%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20news%20media%20and%20nongovernmental%20organisations%20(NGOs)%20reporting%20on%20religious%20minorities%20were%20subjected%20to%20strict%20monitoring%20under%20FCRA%20regulations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20slammed%20the%20US%20commission%20for%20attempting%20to%20%26quot%3Binterfere%26quot%3B%20in%20India's%20electoral%20exercise%20and%20continuing%20to%20indulge%20in%20%26quot%3Bpropaganda%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERandhir%20Jaiswal%2C%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20ministry%2C%20said%20last%20week%20that%20the%20USCIRF%20is%20known%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bbiased%26quot%3B%20entity%20with%20a%20political%20agenda.%20%26quot%3BThe%20US%20Commission%20on%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%20is%20known%20as%20a%20biased%20organisation%20with%20a%20political%20agenda.%20They%20continue%20to%20publish%20their%20propaganda%20on%20India%20masquerading%20as%20part%20of%20an%20annual%20report.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20have%20no%20expectation%20that%20the%20USCIRF%20will%20even%20seek%20to%20understand%20India's%20diverse%2C%20pluralistic%20and%20democratic%20ethos%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaiswal%20said.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20efforts%20to%20interfere%20in%20the%20largest%20electoral%20exercise%20of%20the%20world%20will%20never%20succeed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoscow%20also%20trashed%20allegations%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20an%20Indian%20official%20in%20a%20foiled%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun.%20%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20information%20we%20have%2C%20Washington%20has%20not%20yet%20provided%20any%20reliable%20evidence%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20citizens%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20certain%20GS%20Pannun.%20Speculation%20on%20this%20topic%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20evidence%20is%20unacceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20Zakharova%20said%20at%20the%20briefing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20came%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20report%20in%20The%20Washington%20Post%20that%20cited%20unnamed%20sources%20and%20named%20a%20Research%20and%20Analysis%20Wing%20(RAW)%20officer%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20plot%20to%20kill%20Pannun.%20The%20report%20stated%20that%20India%20is%20trying%20to%20do%20the%20same%20as%20Russia%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20against%20its%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'The%20Washington%20Post'%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20me%2C%20should%20use%20the%20term%20'repressive%20regime'%20and%20everything%20you%20quoted%20in%20relation%20to%20Washington.%20It%20is%20difficult%20to%20imagine%20a%20more%20repressive%20regime%20than%20Washington%2C%20both%20in%20domestic%20and%20international%20affairs%2C%26quot%3B%20Zakharova%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20has%20rejected%20The%20Washington%20Post%20report%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bunwarranted%20and%20unsubstantiated%26quot%3B%20imputation%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%20matter%26quot%3B%20that%20is%20under%20investigation.%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%2C%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20ministry%2C%20termed%20the%20report%20%26quot%3Bspeculative%20and%20irresponsible%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715229300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-03%2F3novmh7c_modi-putin_625x300_21_March_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frussia-says-us-trying-to-destabilise-india-during-lok-sabha-polls-report-5622354%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20aims%20to%20destabilise%20India%20during%20the%202024%20general%20election%2C%20the%20Russian%20foreign%20ministry%20has%20said%20after%20a%20US%20federal%20commission's%20report%20criticised%20New%20Delhi%20for%20alleged%20violations%20of%20religious%20freedom.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frussia-says-us-trying-to-destabilise-india-during-lok-sabha-polls-report-5622354%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frussia-says-us-trying-to-destabilise-india-during-lok-sabha-polls-report-5622354%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frussia-says-us-trying-to-destabilise-india-during-lok-sabha-polls-report-5622354%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Evidence%20That%20India%20Behind%20Khalistan%20Terrorist%20Murder%20Plot%20In%20US%3A%20Russia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERubbishing%20the%20allegations%20by%20the%20US%20on%20India%20for%20a%20foiled%20assassination%20plot%20against%20pro-Khalistan%20radical%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20the%20Russian%20Foreign%20Ministry%20said%20that%20Washington%20has%20not%20yet%20provided%20any%20reliable%20evidence%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20citizens%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20information%20we%20have%2C%20Washington%20has%20not%20yet%20provided%20any%20reliable%20evidence%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20citizens%20in%20the%20preparation%20of%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20certain%20GS%20Pannun.%20Speculation%20on%20this%20topic%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20evidence%20is%20unacceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20spokeswoman%20of%20the%20Russian%20Foreign%20Ministry%2C%20Maria%20Zakharova%20said%20at%20a%20briefing%20on%20Wednesday%20(local%20time).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20the%20US%20does%20not%20understand%20the%20national%20mentality%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20historical%20context%20of%20the%20development%20of%20the%20Indian%20state%20and%20it%20disrespects%20India%20as%20a%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZakharova's%20remarks%20came%20in%20response%20to%20a%20media%20query%20on%20Moscow's%20reaction%20to%20accusations%20against%20an%20Indian%20official%20of%20a%20foiled%20%26quot%3Bassassination%26quot%3B%20plot%2C%20and%20the%20American%20news%20publication%20'The%20Washington%20Post'%20stating%20that%20India%20is%20trying%20to%20do%20the%20same%20as%20Russia%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20against%20its%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'The%20Washington%20Post'%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20me%2C%20should%20use%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Brepressive%20regime%26quot%3B%20and%20everything%20you%20quoted%20in%20relation%20to%20Washington.%20It%20is%20difficult%20to%20imagine%20a%20more%20repressive%20regime%20than%20Washington%2C%20both%20in%20domestic%20and%20international%20affairs.%20Now%20directly%20about%20your%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20Zakharova%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20readout%20of%20the%20briefing%20released%20by%20the%20Russian%20Foreign%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRegular%20unfounded%20accusations%20by%20the%20United%20States%20against%20New%20Delhi%20(we%20see%20that%20they%20groundlessly%20accuse%20not%20only%20India%20but%20also%20many%20other%20states)%20of%20violating%20religious%20freedoms%20are%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20United%20States'%20misunderstanding%20of%20the%20national%20mentality%2C%20the%20historical%20context%20of%20the%20development%20of%20the%20Indian%20state%20and%20disrespect%20for%20India%20as%20a%20state%20.%20I%20am%20sure%20that%20this%20also%20comes%20from%20the%20neocolonial%20mentality%2C%20the%20mentality%20of%20the%20colonial%20period%2C%20the%20period%20of%20the%20slave%20trade%2C%20and%20imperialism%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20does%20not%20only%20apply%20to%20India.%20The%20reason%20is%20the%20desire%20to%20unbalance%20the%20internal%20political%20situation%20in%20India%20in%20order%20to%20complicate%20the%20general%20parliamentary%20elections%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20country.%20Of%20course%2C%20this%20is%20part%20of%20interference%20in%20India's%20internal%20affairs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20is%20an%20India-designated%20terrorist%20who%20holds%20American%20and%20Canadian%20citizenship.%20Earlier%20in%20November%2C%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department%20unsealed%20an%20indictment%20against%20an%20Indian%20national%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20foiled%20plot%20to%20assassinate%20Pannun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%2C%20in%20April%2C%20had%20rejected%20a%20report%20in%20The%20Washington%20Post%20naming%20Indian%20Research%20and%20Analysis%20Wing%20(RAW)%20official's%20involvement%20in%20the%20alleged%20post%20to%20kill%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20it%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bunwarranted%20and%20unsubstantiated%26quot%3B%20imputation%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%20matter%26quot%3B%20that%20is%20under%20investigation%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20official%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20the%20US%20media%20report%20was%20%26quot%3Bspeculative%20and%20irresponsible%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20media%20queries%20on%20the%20report%20that%20appeared%20in%20Washington%20Post%2C%20a%20US%20national%20daily%2C%20Jaiswal%20said%20that%20a%20High-Level%20Committee%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20is%20carrying%20out%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20security%20concerns%20shared%20by%20the%20US%20government%20on%20networks%20of%20organized%20criminals%2C%20terrorists%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20report%20in%20question%20makes%20unwarranted%20and%20unsubstantiated%20imputations%20on%20a%20serious%20matter.%20There%20is%20an%20ongoing%20investigation%20of%20the%20High-Level%20Committee%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20to%20look%20into%20the%20security%20concerns%20shared%20by%20the%20US%20government%20on%20networks%20of%20organised%20criminals%2C%20terrorists%20and%20others.%20Speculative%20and%20irresponsible%20comments%20on%20it%20are%20not%20helpful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20officials%20and%20a%20US%20indictment%2C%20the%20Washington%20Post%20report%20claimed%20that%20the%20RAW%20official%20identified%20as%20Vikram%20Yadav%20had%20directed%20Indian%20businessman%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%20to%20kill%20Pannun%20outside%20his%20New%20York%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%2C%20now%20in%20custody%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20has%20a%20pending%20extradition%20to%20the%20US%20to%20stand%20trial%20in%20the%20case.%20As%20per%20the%20report%20in%20the%20US%20Daily%2C%20the%20operation%20targeting%20Pannun%20was%20approved%20by%20then-RAW%20chief%20Samant%20Goel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20as%20per%20the%20US%20Justice%20Department%20indictment%2C%20Indian%20national%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20custody%2C%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20the%20murder-for-hire%20of%20Pannun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Justice%20Department%20has%20claimed%20that%20Indian%20government%20employee%20(named%20CC-1)%2C%20who%20was%20not%20identified%20in%20the%20indictment%20filed%20in%20a%20federal%20court%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20recruited%20an%20Indian%20national%20named%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20assassination%2C%20which%20was%20foiled%20by%20US%20authorities%2C%20according%20to%20prosecutors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20murder-for-hire%2C%20which%20carries%20a%20maximum%20sentence%20of%2010%20years%20in%20prison.%20Czech%20authorities%20arrested%20and%20detained%20Gupta%20on%20June%2030%2C%20pursuant%20to%20the%20bilateral%20extradition%20treaty%20between%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20Czech%20Republic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20MEA%20said%20that%20a%20case%20filed%20against%20an%20individual%20in%20a%20US%20court%20and%20allegedly%20linking%20him%20to%20an%20Indian%20official%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmatter%20of%20concern%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20contrary%20to%20government%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20also%20set%20up%20a%20high-level%20committee%20to%20probe%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715229060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fl8063v1o_gurpatwant-singh-pannun-twitter_625x300_12_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-evidence-that-india-behind-khalistan-terrorist-murder-plot-in-us-russia-5621819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rubbishing%20the%20allegations%20by%20US%20on%20India%20for%20a%20foiled%20a