s%20regional%20banks%20amid%20a%20coming%20commercial%20real%20estate%20reckoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Starwood%20Capital%20Group%20CEO%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhdRvu0sI3zM%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20he%20thinks%20real%20estate's%20primary%20lenders%20%E2%80%94%20regional%20and%20community%20banks%20%E2%80%94%20could%20soon%20be%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20high%20interest%20rates%20and%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20see%20a%20regional%20bank%20fail%20every%20day%2C%20or%20not%20%E2%80%94%20every%20week%2C%20maybe%20two%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20Sternlicht%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20more%20than%204%2C000%20regional%20and%20community%20banks%20throughout%20the%20US%2C%20many%20of%20which%20may%20not%20have%20the%20cash%20flow%20to%20handle%20major%20loan%20losses%20on%20real%20estate%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProblems%20have%20been%20pummeling%20the%20entirety%20of%20the%20real%20estate%20sector%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcommercial-real-estate-big-trouble-crash-bank-crisis-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommercial%20real%20estate%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20been%20struggling%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20remote%20and%20hybrid%20work%2C%20leading%20to%20more%20and%20more%20vacancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESternlicht%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbarry-sternlicht-recession-us-economy-outlook-real-estate-storm-fed-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eringing%20the%20warning%20bells%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20more%20than%20two%20years%2C%20calling%20the%20situation%20an%20%26quot%3Bexistential%20crisis%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20January%20Bloomberg%20interview.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foffice-crash-property-values-commercial-real-estate-barry-sternlicht-economy-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epredicted%20%241%20trillion%20of%20losses%20on%20office%20properties%20alone.%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20the%20Tuesday%20interview%2C%20Sternlicht%20said%20Fed%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell's%20ongoing%20rate%20hikes%20will%20continue%20to%20have%20consequences%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20sector%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20got%20a%20hard%20task%20with%20a%20blunt%20tool%2C%20and%20the%20consequence%20is%20the%20real%20estate%20markets%20are%20taking%20it%20on%20the%20chin%20because%20rates%20rose%20so%20fast.%20We%20could%20have%20handled%20this%2C%20but%20we%20couldn't%20handle%20it%20this%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20Sternlicht%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%201.9%20trillion%20of%20real%20estate%20loans%2C%20that's%20a%20fragile%20animal%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20one%20regional%20bank%20has%20shuttered%20since%20the%20start%20of%202024.%20Last%20month%2C%20the%20Federal%20Deposit%20Insurance%20Corporation%20seized%20%244%20billion%20in%20deposits%20and%20%246%20billion%20in%20assets%20from%20Republic%20First%20Bank%2C%20a%20regional%20lender%20operating%20in%20the%20Northeast%20with%20significant%20commercial%20real%20estate%20holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20have%20echoed%20Sternlicht's%20warnings.%20Scott%20Rechler%2C%20RXR%20CEO%2C%20made%20a%20similar%20prediction%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20saying%20he%20thinks%20there%20will%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-ceo-scott-rechler-regional-banks-commercial-real-estate-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E500%20fewer%20banks%20in%20the%20US%20by%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20many%20commercial%20real%20estate%20loans%20start%20to%20mature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCommunity%20banks%20are%20important%20to%20our%20fabric%2C%26quot%3B%20Sternlicht%20told%20CNBC%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessins