3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20factor%20to%20consider%20here%20is%20that%2C%20unlike%20US%20policymakers%2C%20the%20UAE%20doesn't%20see%20arms%20purchases%20from%20China%20as%20a%20zero-sum%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20Ahmed%20Aboudouh%2C%20associate%20fellow%20at%20Chatham%20House%20and%20head%20of%20the%20China%20Studies%20Unit%20at%20the%20Emirates%20Policy%20Center%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAbu%20Dhabi's%20first%20choice%20would%20certainly%20be%20to%20acquire%20the%20F-35%20sale%20over%20any%20Chinese%20equivalent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAboudouh%20noted%20that%20approaching%20China%20to%20discuss%20procuring%20advanced%20arms%20is%20driven%20by%20Washington's%20hesitance%20to%20provide%20Abu%20Dhabi%20with%20alternatives%2C%20which%20the%20UAE%20views%20as%20%26quot%3Bcrucial%26quot%3B%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Bnational%20security%20considerations%20and%20high%20regional%20volatility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20French%20multirole%20fighter%20Rafale%20F3R%20Marine%20lands%20on%20the%20tarmac%20of%20the%20Lann-Bihoue%20French%20Navy%20airbase%20in%20western%20France%20on%20January%2012.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65e64533ce7f1785b2e62960%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20UAE%20has%20ordered%2080%20Rafale%20multirole%20fighters%20from%20France's%20Dassault%20Aviation.%20%3Cp%3EFred%20Tanneau%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurthermore%2C%20Abu%20Dhabi%20wants%20its%20%26quot%3Bbalancing%20strategy%26quot%3B%20between%20Washington%20and%20Beijing%20to%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESebastien%20Roblin%2C%20a%20widely%20published%20military-aviation%20journalist%2C%20also%20sees%20Abu%20Dhabi's%20balancing%20act%20in%20play.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20nature%20of%20the%20relationship%20with%20the%20Gulf%20states%20and%20the%20US%20is%20that%20they%20nurture%20secondary%20ties%20with%20China%20and%20Russia%20to%20create%20additional%20pressure%20on%20Washington%20to%20sell%20to%20them%2C%20as%20one%20might%20flirt%20with%20a%20third%20party%20to%20attract%20the%20jealous%20attention%20from%20a%20partner%2C%26quot%3B%20Roblin%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20analysts%20see%20little%20significance%20in%20the%20L-15%20acquisition%20and%20joint%20exercises.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20see%20the%20bilateral%20relations%20between%20the%20air%20forces%20as%20very%20superficial%20and%20symbolic%2C%26quot%3B%20Aboudouh%20said.%20%26quot%3BStrategic%20depth%20in%20military%20partnerships%20takes%20time%20to%20build.%20I%20don't%20see%20this%20relationship%20developing%20into%20something%20similar%20to%20what%20the%20UAE%20Air%20Force%20has%20with%20France%20or%20even%20Russia%20anytime%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERoblin%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20the%20L-15s%20are%20%26quot%3Brespectable%20advanced%20trainers%20sold%20at%20a%20bargain%20unit%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20lack%20the%20benefit%20of%20%26quot%3Bcommon%20systems%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20F-16%20and%20Rafale%20jets%2C%20which%20Emirati%20fighter%20pilots%20will%20eventually%20graduate%20to%20fly.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20Emirati%20air%20force%20fighter%20fleet%20is%20already%20large%20for%20such%20a%20small%20country%2C%20making%20it%20unlikely%20the%20L-15s%20will%20serve%20any%20combat%20role.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BSo%20the%20sale%2C%20like%20the%20common%20exercises%2C%20serves%20as%20a%20warning%20signal%20to%20the%20US%20that%20the%20UAE%20may%20take%20its%20money%20elsewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Roblin%20said.%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20there's%20a%20risk%20of%20that%20backfiring%20and%20convincing%20Washington%20it%20can't%20be%20trusted%20with%20more%20advanced%20US%20h