20move%20to%20his%20village%20permanently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20desire%20to%20reconnect%20with%20his%20roots%2C%20Ashish%20yearned%20to%20look%20after%20his%20ancestral%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F58210%2Ffruit-orchard-destinations-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapple%20orchards%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20were%20lying%20unattended.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20Kinnaur%20is%20known%20worldwide%20for%20its%20apples%2C%20our%20orchards%20were%20abandoned%20as%20there%20were%20no%20young%20members%20in%20my%20family%20to%20look%20after%20them.%20The%20land%20was%20losing%20its%20richness%20and%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20bear%20that.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20prime%20reasons%20why%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-2-1715174392.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashish%20adds%20that%20Kinnauri%20apples%20are%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20ones%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20the%20apple%20growers%20never%20receive%20their%20fair%20share.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-2-1715174392.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-2-1715174392-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-2-1715174392-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-2-1715174392-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FKinnaur-apples-2-1715174392-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349339%5C%22%20height%3D%5C