in%20a%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20love%20was%20nurtured%20over%20time%20and%20she%20decided%20to%20study%20urban%20farming%20and%20nutrition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aditi%20Mali%20of%20Mali%20Greens.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349306%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAditi%20Mali%20of%20Mali%20Greens.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20was%20a%20commerce%20student%20in%20school%20and%20I%20was%20told%20that%20I%20could%20not%20do%20a%20masters%20in%20farming.%20I%20was%20adamant%20and%20wanted%20to%20learn%20urban%20farming%20which%20is%20why%20I%20decided%20to%20look%20for%20colleges%20outside%20India.%20I%20found%20one%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20got%20admitted%20into%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20course%20went%20beyond%20mere%20farming%3B%20it%20delved%20deeply%20into%20the%20nutrition%20we%20require.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20returned%2C%20I%20began%20teaching%20as%20a%20visiting%20faculty%20member%20at%20several%20colleges%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20Watching%20my%20students%20grow%20microgreens%20inspired%20me%20to%20try%20it%20out%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20previously%20her%20work%20and%20life%20got%20in%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20we%20were%20all%20confined%20to%20our%20homes%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20I%20had%20an%20empty%20guest%20room%2C%20which%20I%20converted%20into%20a%20space%20to%20grow%20microgreens%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20the%20whole%20process%20very%20intriguing%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20take%20it%20up%20as%20a%20business.%20I%20decided%20to%20set%20up%20my%20own%20farm%20and%20grow%20microgreens%20commercially.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20Mali%20Greens%20in%202021.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20with%20growing%201%20kg%20of%20microgreens%20at%20home%20and%20now%20my%20farm%20can%20grow%2050%20kg%20of%20microgreens%20in%20one%20harvest%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Aditi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20microgreens%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFalling%20between%20the%20categories%20of%20a%20baby%20green%20and%20a%20sprout%2C%20microgreens%20are%20nutrition-packed%20herbs%20and%20vegetables.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3EHealthline%3C%2Fem%3Earticle%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20often%20contain%20higher%20nutrient%20levels%20than%20more%20mature%20vegetable%20greens.%20This%20makes%20them%20a%20good%20addition%20to%20any%20diet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditi%20believes%20that%20India%20still%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20knowledge%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306361%2Fwhy-is-makhana-expensive-lotus-seeds-fox-nuts-grown-in-bihar-gi-tagged-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabout%20the%20superfood%3C%2Fa%3E%20microgreens.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20am%20at%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20market%20or%20at%20pop-ups%20and%20am%20interacting%20with%20the%20people%2C%20I%20realise%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20unawareness%20among%20them.%20Including%20these%20little%20pockets%20of%20nutrition%20in%20your%20daily%20diet%20can%20really%20do%20wonders%20for%20your%20body.%20They%20contain%20large%20amounts%20of%20vitamins%20B%2C%20K%20and%20C%2C%20folic%20acid%2C%20magnesium%2C%20minerals%20and%20antioxidants%2C%20which%20have%20immense%20health%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20consume%2020-30%20gm%20of%20a%20microgreen%20vegetable%2C%20you%20are%20eating%20double%20the%20nutritional%20value%20of%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20regular%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22She%20grows%20and%20sells%2050%20kgs%20of%20microgreens%20every%20month.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-24-1715159574-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349307%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShe%20grows%20and%20sells%2050%20kg%20of%20microgreens%20every%20month.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditi%20believes%20that%20growing%20microgreens%20with%20the%20right%20tools%20and%20guidance%20can%20be%20done%2C%20adding%20that%20you%20can%20simply%20start%20at%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBehind%20the%20scenes%20of%20growing%20microgreens%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20harvesting%20process%20of%20microgreens%2C%20Aditi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20vertical%20farm%20and%20we%20do%20it%20indoors.%20The%20microgreens%20take%20an%20average%20of%205%20to%207%20days%20to%20grow%2C%20but%20it%20also%20depends%20on%20the%20variety.%20We%20deliver%20them%20according%20to%20the%20demand.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20trials%20and%20errors%2C%20Aditi%20has%20developed%20a%20method.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20chemical-free%20seeds%20to%20grow%20our%20microgreens.%20We%20are%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332094%2Frajasthan-rubi-pareek-doubles-profit-with-organic-farming-gives-free-training%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20very%20organic%20in%20our%20methods%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20do%20not%20use%20any%20pesticides.%20On%20day%20one%2C%20we%20grow%20them%20in%20a%20dark%20room%20and%20once%20they%20sprout%2C%20we%20bring%20them%20to%20the%20light%20room.%20We%20harvest%20only%20on%20demand%20to%20reduce%20wastage.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20ensures%20that%20the%20delivery%20is%20fresh%20and%20natural.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20overproduce%20at%20all%2C%20we%20feed%20it%20to%20stray%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20the%20power-packed%20superfoods%20can%20come%20with%20a%20set%20of%20challenges.%20Talking%20about%20it%2C%20Aditi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20concept%20is%20still%20relatively%20new%2C%20there%20are%20not%20many%20resources%20available%20to%20set%20up%20a%20microgreen%20farm.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20racks%20to%20the%20boxes%2C%20sourcing%20raw%20materials%20was%20challenging.%20We%20repurposed%20trays%20for%20use%20in%20our%20setup.%20For%20the%20soil%2C%20I%20experimented%20with%20different%20combinations%20of%20soils%20and%20cocopeat%20to%20find%20the%20right%20mix%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20trial%20and%20error.%20There%20were%20no%20direct%20predecessors%20to%20learn%20from%2C%20so%20I%20relied%20on%20online%20resources%20and%20YouTube%20videos%20to%20understand%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20a%20balance%20between%20the%20demand%20and%20scaling%20the%20farm%20was%20another%20challenge%20that%20Aditi%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20tricky%20to%20develop%20a%20balance%20between%20demand%20and%20supply%20of%20the%20microgreen.%20We%20are%20still%20learning%20on%20the%20go%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20much%20we%20can%20do%20but%20learn%20from%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20mistakes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThings%20to%20keep%20before%20starting%20a%20microgreens%20business%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Market%20your%20product%20before%20growing%20microgreens%2C%20Aditi%20advises.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20difficult%20to%20make%20people%20understand%20what%20they%20are%20and%20why%20they%20should%20consume%20it.%20Once%20you%20have%20found%20your%20market%2C%20you%20can%20start%20investing%20money%20into%20a%20farm.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCmwlL-PLJS6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCmwlL-PLJS6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%