lar%20to%20Bengaluru%20and%20Pune%2C%20then%20your%20cost%20to%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F301285%2Fmba-grad-kerala-farmer-organic-vegetable-farm-earn-profit-in-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20set%20up%20a%20commercial%20farm%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20somewhere%20around%20Rs%205%20lakh.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20are%20in%20drier%20areas%2C%20the%20cost%20can%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Being%20patient%20is%20the%20key%20to%20growing%20any%20plant%2C%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20microgreens%20do%20not%20take%20much%20time%20to%20grow%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20scope%20for%20things%20to%20go%20wrong.%20And%20things%20will%20go%20wrong%2C%20so%20having%20patience%20and%20doing%20things%20over%20and%20over%20again%20is%20the%20key%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWant%20to%20know%20more%20about%20microgreens%3F%20Visit%20the%20website%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmaligreens.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20picture%20credit%3A%20Aditi%20Mali)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715167223000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fschool-23-1715159570.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349300%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aditi%20Mali%20started%20Mali%20Greens%20to%20increase%20awareness%20about%20microgreens%20and%20their%20nutritional%20benefits.%20With%20over%20900%20consumers%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20she%20has%20been%20growing%20and%20selling%2050%20kg%20of%20microgreens%20every%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%