20was%20around%20this%20time%20that%20French%20writer%2C%20Dominique%20Lapierre%2C%20was%20documenting%20the%20life%20of%20Gaston%20for%20his%20upcoming%20novel.%20When%20Gaston%20relayed%20the%20story%20of%20Wohab%20and%20Pal%20and%20their%20work%20to%20Lapierre%2C%20he%20was%20impressed.%20In%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20looking%20at%20four%20fully-equipped%20boats%20and%20two%20mobile%20emergency%20ambulances%20%E2%80%94%20Lapierre%E2%80%99s%20gift%20to%20their%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20is%20how%20the%20SHIS%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Boat%20Clinic%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%2043%20years%20have%20witnessed%20the%20couple%20extending%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F183217%2Fnayi-disha-community-parents-children-special-needs-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20reach%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20including%20many%20programmes%20under%20its%20ambit.%20These%20include%20a%20tuberculosis%20control%20programme%2C%20an%20eye%20care%20hospital%2C%20a%20school%20for%20girls%2C%20a%20centre%20for%20disabled%20children%20to%20learn%2C%20and%20skill%20development%20programmes%20for%20the%20women%20of%20the%20Sundarbans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20clinic%20that%20comes%20to%20your%20doorstep%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Alam%20elaborates%20on%20the%20joys%20of%20this%20unique%20work%20setup%3B%20even%20as%20the%20fluctuating%20call%20network%20suggests%20the%20remote%20locations%20he%20has%20to%20head%20to%20for%20consultations.%20%E2%80%9CI%20won%E2%80%99t%20disagree%20that%20it%20is%20challenging.%20But%20for%20those%20of%20us%20who%20have%20grown%20up%20in%20the%20Sundarbans%2C%20there%20is%20no%20greater%20joy%20than%20treating%20our%20patients.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%20one%20of%20his%20recent%20cases%20of%20a%20pregnant%20woman.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20gave%20her%20primary%20treatment%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F114009%2Fboat-clinics-brahmaputra-healthcare-boat-clinics-switching-solar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eboat%20clinic%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20she%20needed%20immediate%20attention.%20Since%20we%20do%20not%20undertake%20serious%20medical%20cases%20in%20the%20boat%20clinic%2C%20I%20referred%20her%20to%20the%20nearest%20Government%20hospital.%20We%20arranged%20for%20local%20transport%20to%20get%20her%20there%20and%20she%20delivered%20a%20healthy%20baby.%E2%80%9D%20It%20is%20stories%20like%20these%20that%20make%20him%20smile.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.06.24-PM-1714725063.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Each%20boat%20comprises%20two%20medical%20beds%2C%20a%20mobile%20X-ray%2C%20a%20small%20pathological%20unit%2C%20a%20medical%20store%20room%2C%20and%20an%20oxygen%20cylinder%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.06.24-PM-1714725063.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.06.24-PM-1714725063-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.06.24-PM-1714725063-500x282.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.06.24-PM-1714725063-768x433.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.06.24-PM-1714725063-150x85.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348889%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22722%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3